subfields.a: This latest excursion took her and her companions to Athens, around the Greek mainland, to Chios, and other Aegean islands, to Yugo-slavia, Paris, and London, and an unusual voyage on the Thames.

subfields.c: by Emily Kimbrough ; drawings by Mircea Vasiliu.
